{"tid":1513810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE MOMO其實超有料！穿低胸背心一彎腰「掉出超兇半球」","createTime":"2019-08-28T13:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:12:50.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6c30aec6c0a2f19e25412bedae1a60be76fcc423","tid":1513810,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"TWICE MOMO其實超有料！穿低胸背心一彎腰「掉出超兇半球」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4335/4335608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4335%2F4335608.jpg&h=38521803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMO擁有姣好身材。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／TWICE）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE近期展開世界巡迴演唱會，行程滿檔，日籍成員MOMO近日現身機場時，只見她穿著低胸緊身小背心，下半身搭配高腰褲，上衣短版的設計，讓她露出一截小蠻腰，胸前的傲人上圍也若隱若現，一現身馬上成為焦點之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4335/4335603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4335%2F4335603.jpg&h=65380455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMO穿低胸背心現身機場。（圖／翻攝自Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n而TWICE離開出境大廳的路上，有不少粉絲到場接機，並準備了各種小禮物要送給成員們，當MOMO準備上車前，一名粉絲的牌子意外掉到地上，她一見狀馬上彎腰幫忙撿起掉落的東西，當天穿著低胸背心的她，還將手遮住胸口才彎腰，不過起身時，她的手一放開，就被看到胸前若隱若現的深溝，非常性感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4335/4335602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4335%2F4335602.jpg&h=a99204cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4335/4335601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4335%2F4335601.jpg&h=271d0328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMO彎腰替粉絲撿東西。（圖／翻攝自Twitter）"},{"pid":"4c8fea38b0be2e09e29a478effa418c19e84755a","tid":1513810,"uid":143093,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WUgn95.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WUgn95.gif&h=a7497ee2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d89347ff2d6af187fefe2f5eb585c85097c6283d